{
  "id": "adv_event_2209_01_04",
  "title": "未来とつながるマジカルメロディ 4話 初めての握手会",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hatsune",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……え？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Eh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hatsune",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_04-mku001.m4a",
      "text": "私が、トリエルの握手会に？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Me‚ at the TRINITYAiLE greeting event?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "いい案かもしれないわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It might be a good idea.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_04-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "私達アイドルの活動を知る機会にもなるし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It could be an opportunity for you to learn about our idol activities.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "バーチャル・シンガーやから勝手が違うかもやけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since you're a virtual singer‚ it might be different‚ but",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_04-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "経験積めばその分、表現の幅もきっと広がるやろうし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "With more experience‚ your range of expression will surely expand.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hatsune",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "私、ホログラムだけど出てもいいの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm a hologram‚ but is it okay for me to participate?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hatsune",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_04-mku002.m4a",
      "text": "準備も必要だし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It requires some preparation…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ホログラムの準備は、さほど手間ではないよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Preparing a hologram isn't that much of a hassle.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_04-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "それに、マジカルミライの宣伝も出来るしな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Besides‚ it's an opportunity to promote Magical Mirai.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "助けられてばかりじゃ落ち着かないの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don't feel comfortable being helped all the time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_04-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "イベントの宣伝ぐらいは手伝わせて？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let us help with the event promotion‚ is it okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hatsune",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "みんな……分かった、ありがとう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone… I understand‚ thank you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hatsune",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
